<text>Heatflow, Step 3
How Does KE Spread?

Here lots of atoms that attract each other form a odd-shaped crystal. You can steer one big atom to hit a few atoms and give them energy. Does the KE stay with these few atoms? 

Try the experiment--give the one big atom lots of energy by heating it up with the sun icon in the toolbar. What happens to that energy??

      
       

 


